(339, 1, '2014-01-08 02:12:46', '2014-01-08 02:12:46', '<a href="http://femac.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Tunnel-Pizza4ea120940a0b0515d1d2b6a3ad.pdf">Tunnel Pizza4ea120940a0b0515d1d2b6a3ad</a>', 'Sveba Dahlen Tunnel Pizza Oven', 'veba-Dahlen has developed, marketed and manufactured pizza ovens for over 30 years, and the TP tunnel pizza oven has been produced on the basis of this experience and know-how. The TP is a rapid and compact oven. The use of radiant heat technology allows oven temperature to reach up to 400°C. This allows high capacity and controlled baking of pizzas and other products, for example, pies and pitta bread. Sveba-Dahlen’s TP tunnel pizza oven is available in two sizes, TP-1 and TP-2, with band widths of 585 and 900 mm respectively, both comprises of up to three sections vertically.The baking time required is between 2-10mins. This oven can churn out 500 pizza per hour.\r\n\r\nStandard features:\r\n- Two standard widths up to three section height\r\n- Stainless steel exterior and well-insulated oven chamber\r\n- Easy to use touch screen\r\n- Energy saving mode\r\n- Baking chambers in 2 zones\r\n- Canopies at infeed and outfeed ends\r\n- Removable extraction tray at infeed and outfeed\r\n- Self-cleaning oven chamber\r\n- Stainless steel mesh belt', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'sveba-dahlen-tunnel-pizza-oven', '', '', '2014-01-08 02:13:38', '2014-01-08 02:13:38', '', 0, 'http://femac.com.sg/?post_type=product&#038;p=339', 0, 'product', '', 0),
