(348, 1, '2014-01-08 02:20:20', '2014-01-08 02:20:20', '<a href="http://femac.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/V-Series4ea4cf008be04515d1dbaa6863.pdf">V-Series4ea4cf008be04515d1dbaa6863</a>', 'V-Series', 'The V-series of rack ovens is designed and manufactured to give you the best baking results, reliably and economically. Day and night, year after year.\r\n\r\nIBS, the Sveba-Dahlen patented system for alternating the direction of the rack rotation gives even and effective baking. The patented Cascad steam system incorporated in the V-series produces a powerful, clean and evenly distributed steam supply to give the best baking result.\r\n\r\nStandard Features:\r\n- Available in 3 different sizes\r\n- Ovens of all sizes can be heated by gas, electricity or oil\r\n- Thick insulation allows heat to remain within the oven chamber\r\n- Both exterior and interior of the oven is made out of stainless steel; keep temperature low and enables easy maintenance\r\n- Large door window made out of heat reflecting glass allows one to monitor the entire baking process\r\n- A large effective heat exchanger; quick heating and low energy consumption\r\n- User-friendly control panel\r\n- Double fans enable significant air flow to be distributed evenly inside the oven chamber', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'v-series', '', '', '2014-01-08 02:20:20', '2014-01-08 02:20:20', '', 0, 'http://femac.com.sg/?post_type=product&#038;p=348', 0, 'product', '', 0),
