(769, 1, '2015-07-14 03:01:22', '2015-07-14 03:01:22', '<h3><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-454" src="http://femac.com.sg/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/about-jpg-282x3001.jpg" alt="about-jpg-282x300" width="282" height="300" /></h3>\r\n"Femac is the leading supplier of  bakery equipment and other food processing equipment.\r\n\r\nOur range of equipment includes the followings:\r\n\r\n1) Mixers – Planetary, Spiral &amp; Horizontal Mixers\r\n2) Bread Makeup Equipment – Bun Divider &amp; Rounder, Continuous Divider Rounder System, Industrial bread, pizza &amp; donut production plant.\r\n3) Pastry Equipment – Pastry Sheeters &amp; Pastry production Equipment.\r\n4) Baking Ovens – Deck, Rack &amp; Tunnel Ovens\r\n5) Bake-off Equipment, kitchen equipment and stainless steel equipment\r\n6) Food Encrusting Machine\r\n7) Egg process Equipment – Egg Cracker, Egg White &amp; Yolk Separator, Egg washer &amp; cleaner equipment.\r\n8) Baking Accessories and Baking Utensils – a wide range of baking trays for your baking needs.\r\n\r\nThrough years of experience, we have built up an understanding of our customers and have learnt how to adapt our products to our customers needs.\r\n\r\nBeing in constant touch with our customers and our principles, Femac not only meets the customers'' requirements, and, at the same time, provide practical solutions to our customers.\r\n\r\nFor Femac, success in baking depends on a number of factors. An investment in quality equipment from a reliable supplier cannot be compromised."\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-07-14 03:01:22', '2015-07-14 03:01:22', '', 4, 'http://192.168.1.3:8888/femac-new/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
